Responsibilities : 
5+ years of Maximo experience, ability to lead and coach team in technical aspects of Maximo. Strong communication and troubleshooting skills. 
Ability to identify and implement improvements and the automation of repetitive tasks. 
The Maximo Team Lead will lead and coach a small team of Maximo experts supporting, customizing, and improving Maximo. This person will help improve efficiency, security, and the overall infrastructure design, and streamline TVA support processes in relation to Maximo.
 The primary responsibilities for this role will be to the lead and provide technical guidance to a small team that: 
Requirements : 
Addresses and resolves support incidents. 
Creates database scripts in Oracle 12 
Deploys TVA customizations into the Maximo environment 
Identifies and tests IBM releases or fix packs 
Automates repetitive tasks as much as possible 
Improves documentation and organizes the repository for easy acces 
Review TVAs overall system design and make recommendations for improvement 
